    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0388回】 以「有意識」通往「無意識」</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0301-0400/t-0388-mind-to-void/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Feb 2026 22:44:58 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0301-0400/t-0388-mind-to-void/</guid>
      <description>&lt;style&gt;
  /* 1. 標題縮小 */
